S|Remaining|- **Live re-run** (user-triggered): restart dev server → run a hourbour fix task → confirm `build_gate` + `GraphQuery` + truthful verdict + `learning` events. // - **Hermes sidecar wiring** (optional): run `hermes:setup` on a Docker machine, then wire chosen aux tools. // - **Deferred Part G** (thinking toggle) — not yet built.